iki/pmwiki.php/Creator/GamesWorkshop">Games Workshop</a>.</li><li> <em>The Lord of the Rings: Journeys in Middle-earth</em> (2019) - A boardgame by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/FantasyFlightGames" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/FantasyFlightGames">Fantasy Flight Games</a>.</li><li> <em>The Hobbit: An Unexpected Party</em> (2020) - A game from Weta Workshop set during the opening scenes of <em>An Unexpected Journey</em>.</li></ul><p></p><h2> Video games</h2><ul><li> <em>Shadowfax</em> (1982) - A simple action game where Gandalf rides around and blasts Nazgul, by Postern Ltd.</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheHobbit1982" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheHobbit1982">The Hobbit</a></em> (1982) - An <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction">Interactive Fiction</a> game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse">Melbourne House</a>.</li></ul><ul><li> <em>Lord of the Rings: Game One</em> (1985) - An <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction">Interactive Fiction</a> game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse">Melbourne House</a>.</li><li> <em>The Shadows of Mordor</em> (1987) - An <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InteractiveFiction">Interactive Fiction</a> game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MelbourneHouse">Melbourne House</a>.</li><li> <em>War in Middle Earth</em> (1988) - A <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy">Real-Time Strategy</a> game by <a class="twikilink" h