ideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsTheReturnOfTheKing" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsTheReturnOfTheKing">The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King</a></em> (2003) - An action game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ElectronicArts" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ElectronicArts">Electronic Arts</a>.</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheHobbit2003" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheHobbit2003">The Hobbit</a></em> (2003) - An <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ActionAdventure" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ActionAdventure">Action-Adventure</a> game by Vivendi Universal.</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsWarOfTheRing" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsWarOfTheRing">The Lord of the Rings: War of the Ring</a></em> (2003) - A <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy">Real-Time Strategy</a> game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Sierra" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Sierra">Sierra</a> / <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Vivendi" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Vivendi">Vivendi</a>.</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsTheThirdAge" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheLordOfTheRingsTheThirdAge">The Lord of the Rings: The Third Age</a></em> (2004) - A role-playing game by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ElectronicArts" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/ElectronicArts">Electronic Arts</a>.</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheBattleForMiddleEarth" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheBattleForMiddleEarth">The Battle for Middle-earth</a></em> (2004) - A <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RealTimeStrategy">Real-Time S